{"tid":923164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾楚紅公開反對填海","createTime":"2018-12-01T04:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T12:51:22.000Z","uid":36544,"like":607,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"07ab40e98557cce7935f7e2274bbd9cfc47c23fd","tid":923164,"uid":36544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T04:46:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/鍾楚紅公開反對填海/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E9%8D%BE%E6%A5%9A%E7%B4%85%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%A1%AB%E6%B5%B7%2F&d=IGUMcHggKeeOZ9hQ12bYrTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=1e18691f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E9%8D%BE%E6%A5%9A%E7%B4%85%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%A1%AB%E6%B5%B7%2F&h=88de8efd\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/鍾楚紅公開反對填海/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/chung_eHPnM_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fchung_eHPnM_1200x0.png&h=d5b85656&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n58歲的香港女星鍾楚紅，今日出席活動時突然開腔反對填海，更稱大埔元朗有新多農地空置，「唔係起樓，空曬係度好似垃圾堆」，覺得非常浪費，「我覺得好浪費，我寧願佢善用啲地起樓，好過填海，因為我好反對填海」。<br />\n<br />\n鍾楚紅本來是和記者分享自己喜歡有機、新鮮食材，但香港本土有機食材供應不足，「就算想買本地農產品都唔容易」，認為政府可以考慮補貼香港農業之餘，善用荒廢農地，之後話鋒一轉，談及自己行山時經常看到新界有荒廢農地非常浪費，希望政府好好利用這些荒廢地發展本地農業和建屋，認為是「一舉兩得」。"},{"pid":"7fff041b977a034f54d2fc259413e9ac9e707807","tid":923164,"uid":84633,"like":86,"dislike":1,"score":85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T04:47:01.000Z","msg":"58<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4772db4df5fffd8df5fff27a70455983f3f8816","tid":923164,"uid":50457,"like":236,"dislike":6,"score":230,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T04:47:21.000Z","msg":"境然有人講真話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8c94a6e14c168cd6b88b84e9dd1510ad270e9d","tid":923164,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T04:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dceb26b43ffd7436a3bf3cf81a249339ec684bb0","tid":923164,"uid":202464,"like":303,"dislike":0,"score":303,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T04:50:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>境然有人講真話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地都唔使返支那搵錢。自然識講人話。"},{"pid":"ba396fe3cc785c5bdaa49cbaa9014a8665f1a2a1","tid":923164,"uid":139700,"like":167,"dislike":0,"score":167,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T04:51:06.000Z","msg":"劉德華係咪潛咗水?冇跟開"},{"pid":"7bb6ef28aee45058873c93e1fe8d183a7b03ee74","tid":923164,"uid":119234,"like":190,"dislike":0,"score":190,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T04:53:22.000Z","msg":"佢後生果時，真係靚得好誇張"},{"pid":"feb625ae2a1b3c8be61d45c76ed32bfd24cca365","tid":923164,"uid":48083,"like":133,"dislike":0,"score":133,"quote":{"pid":"7bb6ef28aee45058873c93e1fe8d183a7b03ee74","tid":923164,"uid":119234,"like":190,"dislike":0,"score":190,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T04:53:22.000Z","msg":"佢後生果時，真係靚得好誇張"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T04:57:01.000Z","msg":"依家都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205477b96e37707acb2b80b42ae91978e2ca2fc1","tid":923164,"uid":23833,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T04:58:34.000Z","msg":"58我屌<br />\n<br />\n女人味濃"},{"pid":"bf23d8fd124e57ac2e0c6cccb9905773e79ddd70","tid":923164,"uid":5919,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T04:59:37.000Z","msg":"殺手雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s